Caitlin Greer https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Caitlin_Greer 0 Caitlin Greer (born 20th century) is an American actress and voice-over artist. Her voice was used in Rockstar Games' Bully as Beatrice Trudeau. She is the narrator of The New York Times-bestselling Hush, Hush novel by Becca Fitzpatrick. She has narrated many other books, but Hush, Hush, is her most known work. Caitlin_Greer ( born 20th_century ) is an_American_actress and voice-over_artist .
